  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>HTML5 Canvas 2D — no external dependencies</li>
    <li>Mouse &amp; touch drag interaction</li>
    <li>Thin lens equation · ray tracing · responsive scaling</li>
    <li>Source: <code>Bootcamp-test/apps/convex-lens-simulator/public/script.js</code></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- The canvas element is here ready for the script to use -->
<canvas
